verses.text:
Things that exist now have already existed previously,
\q2 and things that will happen in the future have already happened previously;
\q2 God causes us to want to understand mysteries.

If people think sensibly, it will lead them to do what is right;
\q2 if they think foolishly, it causes them to do what is wrong.
\q1

Give generously to others some of the money that you have;
\q2 if you do that, later you will get back an equal amount.
\q1
